data.description: Buyers contingency fell through and now it’s your chance!!—If you are looking for a big family home, this is the one for you! Plenty of space for the entire family. Separate primary bedroom downstairs with separate shower and tub, dual sinks and a walk-in closet. 4 bedrooms 2.5 baths with 2 dining areas, one could be used as an office, with another room for possibly a game room or family room upstairs. Updated, modern ceiling fans. Spacious backyard with a garden area. You won't find another home like this, in this location at such a great deal! The neighborhood is family friendly and offers a pond and play area. Easy and quick access to highways, shopping and restaurants. Come check out this home today!
